noncvs.documentDescription: This document details the files that are kept in the vegbank noncvs directory. These are not in CVS, but are still essential to backup and required for the site to function properly. Changes to documents (additions, deletions) can also be viewed by tracking this document in CVS.

file.name: archive/vegbank2004purge.tar.gz
file.description: Files eliminated from cvs in 2004. Kept in case there is something we need here.

file.name: data/insert_preload_ANSI.sql.gz
file.description: The SQL used to insert the preloaded data. As long as the database stays backed up, this is probably not needed.

file.name: panel/mou.pdf
file.description: MOU with VegBank and various other orgs
